    "created_at": "2015-08-04T07:03:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-04T07:03:05Z",
    "body": "The `preload` script is simply implemented by calling `require('script/path')`, if you want to allow users to setup their own preload scripts, I think the best way is to just implement it by calling `require` in your preload script.\n"
